        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued April 19 at 5:54PM CDT until April 19 at 6:15PM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 553 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 8 miles east of
McCamey, moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Law enforcement reported quarter size hail near McCamey at
550 PM CDT.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
McCamey and Upton County Airport.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
